## Repository pattern

This project uses the repository pattern. Delegate to `self._repo`:
- list:   `return await self._repo.list(**filters)`
- get:    `return await self._repo.get(id)`  (repo raises not-found if missing)
- create: `return await self._repo.create(data)`
- update: `return await self._repo.update(id, data)`
- delete: `await self._repo.delete(id)`
{% elif services_pattern == "domain" %}

## Domain model pattern

Translate between persistence entities and Pydantic domain models:
1. Fetch entity via ORM/repo
2. Map to the Pydantic return type before returning
